<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>I HAVE HEARD OF A LAND FAR AWAY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginna'n gamnuom a um tih ka hei,
 A lopi zie gentheih guolloh chuh;
 Kumsawt a In ni sanga vakah,
 Ziechun Isu tawh um ka nuom hi.

[V2]
 Um ka nuom, um ka nuom!
 Ziechun Isu tawh um ka nuom hi;
 Um ka nuom, um ka nuom!
 Ziechun Isu tawh um ka nuom hi.

[V3]
 2. Pathien Lehkhabu thu ka sim leh!
 Vangpiekna chuh mun ka kipak hi;
 Gilkiel leh dangchak umta puo'n a,
 Ziechun hatlote chuh chawl ta'n au.

[V4]
 3. Van-gam nawpzie kuo-a gen thei ding?
 Thavaihna, lungkhamna bei tana;
 Mithi ngaia kahna natna tawh,
 Thihna him um kit thei ta puo'n a.

[V5]
 4. Zie gam nuomtak achun um dingin,
 Pathien in mi gilote A chiel;
 Kuole A chielna ngailulte chuh,
 Zie gam nuomtak achun cheng un au.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>380</hymn_number>
</song>